sources.title: The White Gorilla (Adventure, 1945) with Ray Corrigan, Lorraine Miller & George J. Lewis | Movie
sources.description:
The Unconscious FORM Of A Girl Puzzled Him!
A white gorilla causes trouble in the deepest heart of Africa. The film uses footage from the silent 1927 serial Perils Of The Jungle which was written by director of The White Gorilla Harry L Fraser under the name Harry P.Crist

Director & Writer: Harry L. Fraser 
Stars: Ray Corrigan, Lorraine Miller, George J. Lewis
Genres: Classics, Adventure 
CCC side note: (not to be confused with White Pongo) https://youtu.be/1R6jSub-f8g
